    {
      "id": "error-card-schema-examples",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "9. Examples",
      "position": {
        "x": 1780,
        "y": -60
      },
      "width": 560,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Example Cards\n\n- **Missing Target Card**\n  Shows the missing `sourceRef` or bad `sourceNodeId`.\n- **Missing Binding Card**\n  Shows that a typed node is missing its class-instance contract.\n- **Unavailable Payload Card**\n  Shows that the target exists but does not expose the requested `node.web.*` payload.\n- **Authority Reduced Card**\n  Shows that the host asked for more than effective authority allows.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
