      "width": 560,
      "height": 300,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Adoption Notes\n\nStart by routing current blank-shell cases through shared error cards:\n\n1. missing preview target\n2. missing class-instance binding\n3. missing consumed payload\n4. authority-reduced preview fallback\n\nLater, decide which of these belong in browser mode versus editor-only authoring mode.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
