    {
      "id": "error-card-schema-human-notes",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "12. Human Notes",
      "position": {
        "x": -1820,
        "y": -60
      },
      "width": 560,
      "height": 280,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Failure Points\n\nLikely first-wave failures for shared error cards:\n\n1. Missing or stale `sourceNodeId` on a consumed surface.\n2. Missing `sourceRef` or an unreachable target graph.\n3. View provider exists but does not expose the requested payload.\n4. Class-backed instance is missing `_classBinding`, `_bridge`, or `definitionKey`.\n5. Bridge or port resolves, but the target view or preview payload is unavailable.\n6. Local policy or authority reduces the requested surface below what the host expected.\n\nThese failures should stay visible on-canvas rather than collapsing into blank rectangles.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
